<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وبَلغْن:</span> البلاغة.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والفَرْدد:</span> مكان صلب غليظ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وشُرْبُب:</span> موضع.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والعُنْدَد:</span> البد.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والرِمْدِد:</span> الرماد.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والمعَدّ:</span> ما يصيبه عقبُ الراكب من جنب الفرس.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والخِدبّ:</span> الغليظ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والفِلِز:</span> ما كان من جواهر المعادن على خلقته الأولى.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أُدَابر:</span> لا يقبل موعظة.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>